data.description: Welcome to this charming 2 bedroom, 1 full bathroom raised ranch nestled in the heart of West Creek on Dock Road. Boasting an amazing location, this home features a large deck overlooking nature's splendor. Imagine waking up to the tranquil sights and sounds of turtles, birds, and waterfowl right in your own yard. With no bulkhead required, as per the prior owner, you can fully immerse yourself in the beauty of the surroundings. Across the way lies a protected wildlife refuge, offering a serene backdrop for your daily life. From sunrise to sunset, and every moment in between, you'll be treated to breathtaking views from both the front and back of the house. This area exudes a quiet, non-commercialized atmosphere, providing that quintessential small-town feel. Go outside and hop on your kayak to explore the stunning scenery or venture out to the Great Bay for fishing and crabbing adventures just minutes from your doorstep. Experience the magic of waterfront living in this unparalleled retreat.
